Any claims made outside of this period are at our absolute discretion. We will not accept items if you change your mind, as per Fair Trading guidelines. Goods must be returned in original brand new, un-used condition. It is your responsibility to make sure that the goods make it to us, any items lost in the post are not our responsibility.
